config:
credentials:
- name: container-registry-estafette
  type: container-registry
  password: ***
  private: false
  repository: estafette
  username: ***
- name: container-registry-extensions
  type: container-registry
  password: ***
  private: false
  repository: extensions
  username: ***
- name: gke-development
  type: kubernetes-engine
  cluster: development-europe-west1-c
  defaults:
    autoscale:
      min: 1
    container:
      repository: estafette
    namespace: development
    sidecar:
      image: estafette/openresty:1.13.6.1-alpine
      type: openresty
  project: estafette-development
  region: europe-west1
  serviceAccountKeyfile: ***
  zone: europe-west1-c
- name: gke-staging
  type: kubernetes-engine
  cluster: staging-europe-west1-c
  defaults:
    autoscale:
      min: 2
    container:
      repository: estafette
    namespace: staging
    sidecar:
      image: estafette/openresty:1.13.6.1-alpine
      type: openresty
  project: estafette-staging
  region: europe-west1
  serviceAccountKeyfile: ***
  zone: europe-west1-c
- name: gke-production
  type: kubernetes-engine
  cluster: production-europe-west1-c
  defaults:
    autoscale:
      min: 3
    container:
      repository: estafette
    namespace: production
    sidecar:
      image: estafette/openresty:1.13.6.1-alpine
      type: openresty
  project: estafette-production
  region: europe-west1
  serviceAccountKeyfile: ***
  zone: europe-west1-c
- name: slack-webhook-estafette
  type: slack-webhook
  webhook: ***
  workspace: estafette
